snippet.textDisplay:
As a Tamilian, and listened to A R Rahman for almost 20 yrs, and despite knowing all his versatility, creativity and his range of classical Hindustani and Carnatic ragas he has operated across his career, this  classical music, this one truly. Ladies and Gentlemen, we are truly listening to a surprisingly rare composition from A. R. Rahman. 

For one, throughout his career he has rarely composed any classical music in Hindustani Yaman Raga or Carnatic Kalyani Raga. Maybe Rajnikanth's Baba song 'Sakthi Kodu' was one. That was it. 
Thank You Rahman sir for making my wish complete. Since it is my favourite Raga and is such a mystic Raag in the way it enslaves the hearts like a Queen Enchantress. I am so glad you finally did compose one. 😍😍
